%h2 Editing Network Governance

%fieldset{:style => 'width: 270px; height: 95px; float: left; margin-right: 25px;'}
  %legend Annual Meeting Appointments
  %p Are appointments made during the Annual Meeting?
  %ol.radio_button_list
    %li= default_form.radio_button :sg_annual_meeting_appointments, true, {:li_class => 'radio_button', :label => 'Yes', :label_for => :local_network_sg_annual_meeting_appointments_true}
    %li= default_form.radio_button :sg_annual_meeting_appointments, false, {:li_class => 'radio_button', :label => 'No', :label_for => :local_network_sg_annual_meeting_appointments_false}


%fieldset{:style => 'width: 270px; height: 95px;'}
  %legend Positions Appointed
  %ol.checkbox_list{:style => 'padding-top: 10px;'}
    = default_form.check_box :sg_selected_appointees_local_network_representative, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Network Representative'} 
    = default_form.check_box :sg_selected_appointees_steering_committee, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Steering Committee'} 
    = default_form.check_box :sg_selected_appointees_contact_point, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Contact Person'} 

%div.hint_toggle
  About the Governance Document...
%div.hint_text{:style => 'display: none; width: 600px;'}
  %p It is required for governance accountability to upload a document containing a brief description of how the Network Representative and Steering Committee derive their mandate.

%fieldset{:style => 'width: 600px; height: 50px;'}
  %legend Governance Document
  %ol
    %li=default_form.file_field :sg_annual_meeting_appointments_file_id, {:li_class => 'file', :label => 'Select a PDF to upload'}
    
%div.hint_toggle
  Steering committees...
%div.hint_text{:style => 'display: none; width: 600px;'}
  %p Members of a steering committee should have solid standing and reputation in their countries. They should also have a sound understanding of the Global Compact's philosophy and work to implement the Ten Principles in a spirit of competence, respect and integrity while pursuing commercial interests.

%fieldset{:style => 'width: 600px;'}
  %legend Stakeholder Groups Involved in Governance

  %ol.checkbox_list{:style => 'float: left; margin-left: -25px; margin-right: 20px;'}
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_company, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Companies'} 
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_sme, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'SMEs'} 
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_business_association, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Business Associations'} 

  %ol.checkbox_list{:style => 'float: left; margin-right: -20px;'}
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_labour, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Labour'} 
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_un_agency, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'UN Agencies'} 
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_ngo, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'NGOs'} 

  %ol.checkbox_list{:style => 'float: left;'}
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_foundation, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Foundations'} 
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_academic, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Academic Institutions'} 
    = default_form.check_box :stakeholder_government, {:li_class => 'checkbox', :label => 'Government Entities'} 
